# Bang Web Server Meta Dweeb Configuration File

<Package>
    Name        bang-web-server
    Version     @VERSION@
    Maintainer  Bang Developers <bang-dev@threerings.net>
    Section     pages
    Architecture    all
    Description A meta package that depends on packages needed for a Bang web server

    # Maintainer Scripts
    # See http://www.debian.org/doc/debian-policy/ch-maintainerscripts.html
    PreInstall      @SCRIPTPATH@/bang-web-server-preinst

    Depends     bang-pages
    Depends     bang-installer (= @VERSION@)
    Depends     bang-applet (= @VERSION@)
    Depends     bang-client-current (= @VERSION@)
    Depends     office-webapp (= @VERSION@)
    # not strictly a dependency, but needed in current web configuration 
    Depends     bang-hemiptera-map (= @VERSION@)
</Package>
